creator: Meetup
descriptionHtml:
Get connected with local groups hosting online events so you can meet new people and try new things. Use Meetup to build your career, find support, get out of your comfort zone, or pursue a passion. Download the app to discover online events hosted by local groups, or start a group to schedule your own online events.

Discover local online events and groups
- Get matched with online events based on your interests, from book clubs to free yoga and more
- Explore groups hosting online events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area
- Save events you’re interested in and revisit them later
- Use discussions and messaging to stay in touch with the people you meet

Start a group
- Host your own online events by creating a group for whatever you’re into
- Watch your community grow as your group is recommended to interested people
- Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-fly, and manage your group from anywhere
- Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and messaging to connect with the people in your group

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet new people, do new things

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We’re always making improvements so Meetup works better for you. Get the latest version for all of the available features.

As always, we love hearing your feedback: androiddev@meetup.com

So... we're back to providing useful release notes. Thank you for the feedback. We appreciate it and we'll do better. Please keep the comments coming. It makes us and the app better.

Bug fixes
- copying a past event should no longer strand you behind a spinner
- we removed the "join now" option for past events because #facepalm

Oh... and Dark Mode. Our team may be more excited than you that we've finally got this out. Thanks for your patience, making us better and for being part of Meetup!

title: Meetup: Find events near you

creator: Meetup
descriptionHtml:
Discover the things you love to do and people to do it with both online and in person. With over 50 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, and pursue your passions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events happening every week.

Discover local and online events


• Get matched with over 330,000 groups based on your interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
• Explore events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area
• Save events you’re interested in and revisit them later
• Have discussions and use direct messaging to stay in touch with the people you meet

Start a group


• Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic
• Watch your community grow as your group is recommended to interested people
• Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-fly, and manage your group from anywhere
• Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and messaging to connect with the people in your group

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).

- Other style and minor fixes

title: Meetup: Find events near you

creator: Meetup
descriptionHtml:
Discover the things you love to do and people to do it with both online and in person. With over 50 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, and pursue your passions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events happening every week.

Discover local and online events


• Get matched with over 330,000 groups based on your interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
• Explore events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area
• Save events you’re interested in and revisit them later
• Have discussions and use direct messaging to stay in touch with the people you meet

Start a group


• Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic
• Watch your community grow as your group is recommended to interested people
• Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-fly, and manage your group from anywhere
• Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and messaging to connect with the people in your group

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet new people, do new things

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
You can now RSVP and attend in-progress events, one of our most user-requested features to support online events.

Did we miss something? We love hearing your feedback: androiddev@meetup.com

title: Meetup: Find events near you

creator: Meetup
descriptionHtml:
Discover the things you love to do and people to do it with both online and in person. With over 50 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, and pursue your passions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events happening every week.

Discover local and online events


• Get matched with over 330,000 groups based on your interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
• Explore events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area
• Save events you’re interested in and revisit them later
• Have discussions and use direct messaging to stay in touch with the people you meet

Start a group


• Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic
• Watch your community grow as your group is recommended to interested people
• Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-fly, and manage your group from anywhere
• Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and messaging to connect with the people in your group

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet new people, do new things

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release removes support for OS versions below API 24 (7.0). Limiting the number of OS versions we support enables us to provide a higher quality Android experience. We’ve also made some under-the-hood improvements to keep things running smoothly.

App feedback is always welcome: androiddev@meetup.com

title: Meetup: Find events near you

creator: Meetup
descriptionHtml:
Discover the things you love to do and people to do it with both online and in person. With over 50 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, and pursue your passions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events happening every week.

Discover local and online events


• Get matched with over 330,000 groups based on your interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
• Explore events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area
• Save events you’re interested in and revisit them later
• Have discussions and use direct messaging to stay in touch with the people you meet

Start a group


• Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic
• Watch your community grow as your group is recommended to interested people
• Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-fly, and manage your group from anywhere
• Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and messaging to connect with the people in your group

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet new people, do new things

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
With this release, we are improving the way members can search for events. We are also continuing to fix bugs to make the Meetup experience better for every member.

App feedback is always welcome: androiddev@meetup.com

With over 50 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, and pursue your passions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events happening every week.

Discover local and online events


• Get matched with over 330,000 groups based on your interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
• Explore events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area
• Save events you’re interested in and revisit them later
• Have discussions and use direct messaging to stay in touch with the people you meet

Start a group


• Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic
• Watch your community grow as your group is recommended to interested people
• Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-fly, and manage your group from anywhere
• Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and messaging to connect with the people in your group

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet new people, do new things

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Organizers are now able to schedule events with COVID 19 restrictions, from mask to vaccination requirements. We are working to make Meetup experiences safer for everyone - more to come!

App feedback is always welcome: androiddev@meetup.com

Discover the things you love to do and people to do it with both online and in person. With over 50 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, and pursue your passions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events happening every week.

Discover local and online events


• Get matched with over 330,000 groups based on your interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
• Explore events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area
• Save events you’re interested in and revisit them later
• Have discussions and use direct messaging to stay in touch with the people you meet

Start a group


• Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic
• Watch your community grow as your group is recommended to interested people
• Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-fly, and manage your group from anywhere
• Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and messaging to connect with the people in your group

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet new people, do new things

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
You will now be able to view all of your Event chats in the Messages tab. Your direct messages are still there, but now you can go back and forth between DMs and Event chat.

App feedback is always welcome: androiddev@meetup.com

title: Meetup: Social Groups & Events

creator: Meetup
descriptionHtml:
Pursue your interests with people who share them, both online and in person. With over 60 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, make time for your hobbies, and meet friends who share similar interests.

Easily meet people you know you’ll get along with and create groups of friends that will be as excited as you to embrace your hobbies, participate in online or local events or engage in discussions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events with new people happening every week.

Discover local and online events

👥 Meet new people and get matched with over 330,000 groups and friends based on your network of interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
🗺 Explore online or local events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area with a map
👍 Save events you’re interested in and come back to them later. Pick and choose the people and friends you want to meet at all the events that you like
🗣 Have discussions with the people you meet and use direct messaging to stay in touch with your new friends
🎈 Meet people who are interested in the same local or online events, create new groups of friends and expand your online network

Start a group

👋 Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic, and meet friends who wants to participate
👤 Watch your community of friends and network of people grow as your group is recommended to interested people and potential new friends to meet
🗓 Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-go, and manage your group from anywhere
💬 Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and instant messaging to connect with the people and friends in your group that you are keen to meet

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).

This release also includes some under-the-hood improvements to keep things running smoothly.

title: Meetup: Social Events & Groups

creator: Meetup
descriptionHtml:
Pursue your interests with people who share them, both online and in person. With over 60 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, make time for your hobbies, and meet friends who share similar interests.

Easily meet people you know you’ll get along with and create groups of friends that will be as excited as you to embrace your hobbies, participate in online or local events or engage in discussions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events with new people happening every week.

Discover local and online events

👥 Meet new people and get matched with over 330,000 groups and friends based on your network of interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
🗺 Explore online or local events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area with a map
👍 Save events you’re interested in and come back to them later. Pick and choose the people and friends you want to meet at all the events that you like
🗣 Have discussions with the people you meet and use direct messaging to stay in touch with your new friends
🎈 Meet people who are interested in the same local or online events, create new groups of friends and expand your online network

Start a group

👋 Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic, and meet friends who wants to participate
👤 Watch your community of friends and network of people grow as your group is recommended to interested people and potential new friends to meet
🗓 Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-go, and manage your group from anywhere
💬 Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and instant messaging to connect with the people and friends in your group that you are keen to meet

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet people, make friends: Join a club, event, community, local or online groups

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes some under-the-hood improvements to keep things running smoothly.

App feedback is always welcome: androiddev@meetup.com

Pursue your interests with people who share them, both online and in person. With over 60 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, make time for your hobbies, and meet friends who share similar interests.

Easily meet people you know you’ll get along with and create groups of friends that will be as excited as you to embrace your hobbies, participate in online or local events or engage in discussions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events with new people happening every week.

Discover local and online events

👥 Meet new people and get matched with over 330,000 groups and friends based on your network of interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
🗺 Explore online or local events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area with a map
👍 Save events you’re interested in and come back to them later. Pick and choose the people and friends you want to meet at all the events that you like
🗣 Have discussions with the people you meet and use direct messaging to stay in touch with your new friends
🎈 Meet people who are interested in the same local or online events, create new groups of friends and expand your online network

Start a group

👋 Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic, and meet friends who wants to participate
👤 Watch your community of friends and network of people grow as your group is recommended to interested people and potential new friends to meet
🗓 Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-go, and manage your group from anywhere
💬 Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and instant messaging to connect with the people and friends in your group that you are keen to meet

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet local people, make friends & network: Join a community, group, host events

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Introducing new profiles for Meetup. Profiles provide a better sense of who will be there at your next event.

App feedback is always welcome: androiddev@meetup.com

Easily meet people you know you’ll get along with and create groups of friends that will be as excited as you to embrace your hobbies, participate in online or local events or engage in discussions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events with new people happening every week.

Discover local and online events

👥 Meet new people and get matched with over 330,000 groups and friends based on your network of interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
🗺 Explore online or local events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area with a map
👍 Save events you’re interested in and come back to them later. Pick and choose the people and friends you want to meet at all the events that you like
🗣 Have discussions with the people you meet and use direct messaging to stay in touch with your new friends
🎈 Meet people who are interested in the same local or online events, create new groups of friends and expand your online network

Start a group

👋 Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic, and meet friends who wants to participate
👤 Watch your community of friends and network of people grow as your group is recommended to interested people and potential new friends to meet
🗓 Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-go, and manage your group from anywhere
💬 Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and instant messaging to connect with the people and friends in your group that you are keen to meet

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: androiddev@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).
descriptionShort: Meet local people, make friends & network: Join a community, group, host events
